N = int(input())
A = [int(i) for i in input().split()]

for i in range(N):
    print(A.index(i+1)+1, end=' ')

def main():
    n = int(input())
    a = list(map(int, input().split()))
    b = list(enumerate(a, 1))
    b = sorted(b, key=lambda x: x[1])
    b = [i[0] for i in b]
    print(*b, sep='\n')


if __name__ == '__main__':
    main()
